{"tid":897423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男大生「一夜2次」遭控性侵　小女友哭：剛穿好褲子他又要","createTime":"2018-11-11T01:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T01:55:27.000Z","uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d436762b288a8294dc912a075f0deae308517eaa","tid":897423,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T01:29:13.000Z","msg":"年輕人不要太衝動！<br />\n<br />\n《聯合報》報導，桃園市某陳姓大學生(22歲)2年多前透過臉書認識一名女高中生，兩人交往1個多月後，男生帶女生回租屋處親熱「一夜2次」，被女方母親發現後提告性侵。<br />\n<br />\n法官查閱女方與女性友人對話紀錄，女生向友人哭訴：「他剛做完、我才穿好褲子沒多久，又要第二次」、「我一直拉住褲子、他一扯就掉了」...等，但陳男室友作證表示，有看到陳男和女生親熱，2人中途還變換姿勢，並沒聽到女生喊不要。<br />\n<br />\n法官根據雙方說法，且發現兩人事後還有聯絡，認定不是性侵，但陳男與女友發生關係時，女生當時未滿16歲，法官依2個「妨害性自主罪」判陳男8個月徒刑，且未宣告緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20181111/1464292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20181111%2F1464292%2F&d=w5dhjXZP8%2BCC%2Ft1jVEv2cKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=21239989\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20181111%2F1464292%2F&h=f9b26c2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20181111/1464292/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b378a9b0f01402a3b16b57f105dfb82b3a5c9d","tid":897423,"uid":41961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"陳男室友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382af74ed122c2289a16b15d9f9d5fba0b844dbe","tid":897423,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"姓陳果然淫底"},{"pid":"87c888b15009e8f550871158bc1c10ca0ad5eae5","tid":897423,"uid":191762,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"睇標題都估到係台灣"},{"pid":"468e787575a23155652496d30fe540467d57ad28","tid":897423,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"